column1: Sleek

column4:
this women’s watch is a definite choice for any of your casual get-togethers.

Body and Design

column1: The Sonata Yuva Gold Analog Watch sports a contemporary dial that houses an attractively coloured watch face. The dial’s background has a subtle pattern so as to eliminate any sense of monotony. As part of the distinctive design
column2: the dial on this women’s analog watch features only six hour markers which are on the 3
column3: 4 and 5-hour positions on the right and the 9
column4: 10 and 11-hour positions on the left side of the dial. These hour markers along with the watch’s three time indicating hands have a sophisticated metallic finish
column5: which against the deep colour of the watch face provides for easy and trouble-free time reading.

column1:
The stylish and contemporary dial on this Sonata Yuva Gold watch is enveloped in a sturdy case with the same metallic finish as the watch hands and the hour markers. This case not only adds to the watch’s high aesthetic value but also provides the all-important dial with a much needed level of durability and protection.

Functions and Other Features

All the changes and adjustments that you wish to make to the positions of the watch hands can easily be accomplished with the rotating crown located on the right side of the dial’s case. This metallic case has extensions at the top and bottom portions forming lugs that serve the purpose of attaching it to the watch’s extremely attractive leather strap. The leather strap helps keep this Yuva Gold analog watch from Sonata comfortably attached to your wrist as long as your need. The dial’s sturdy case combines with a hardy clear glass cover to give the watch the ability to be water-resistant up to a depth of 30 m.
Boasting a high level of <strong>aesthetics
column3: this personal timekeeper from Sonata’s Yuva Gold series gives its wearer a highly improved sense of style and sophistication
column4: while also providing great flaunt value.

column1: The Sonata Yuva Analog watch is the true essence of femininity and gives you a beautiful accessory to pair with your clothes. column1: This extremely stylish and classy timepiece comes from Casio’s highly rated and popular range of casual analog watches for women. Featuring the most essential function of timekeeping
column2: this battery powered watch from Casio is sure to always help you keep track of time
column3: all the while adding substantial value to your style quotient. The timekeeping function on this watch runs on the popular quartz crystal technology
column4: which uses small bar shaped crystals of quartz or silicon dioxide as it is otherwise referred to as.

column1: The functioning of the Quartz timepieces like this Casio analog women’s watch makes use of quartz crystals to provide a very accurate resonator which gives a constant electronic signal for timekeeping purposes. These quartz crystals work by generating an electrical charge which causes them to vibrate at a thousand times a second
column2: making them extremely stable resonators for extremely accurate timekeeping. The biggest advantage of employing this quartz crystal technology is its operational simplicity and accuracy
column3:
while the entire manufacturing process remains relatively cost effective.

column3: making them very easily visible against the dial’s dark background. This very thoughtful colour combination used on the dial makes it very easy to gauge the time with just a single glance at the dial.

column1: This dial is surrounded by a considerably sturdy stainless steel case which provides the dial with sizeable protection against low intensity impacts and shock. The time displayed on the watch face can easily be adjusted or changed by using the watch’s rotating crown which is located on the right side of the dial’s stainless steel case.

The entire dial and case configuration on this watch is held firmly on your wrist with a very impressive and effective stainless steel bracelet strap. This stainless steel strap with a 21 mm band width sports a very similar look and finish as the dial’s case and the watch hands
column2: making most of the elements that comprise this watch aesthetically well matched.

column1: Apart from the stainless steel case

column1: Nature is mankind’s greatest source of artistic inspiration and results in something truly beautiful. A perfect example for nature inspired creativity would be the Casio Sheen Analog Watch for Women that has drawn inspiration from the stunning night sky that is studded with stars. This charmingly elegant watch is for the woman whose personality is as bright as star
column2:
whose generosity is as radiant like the moon but whose core is as tough as steel. The multi-purpose Sheen Analog sports Watch is the perfect accessory to pair with your casual and formal clothes and even great for those high-fashion clothes you sport from time to time.

Body and Design

column1:
The battery powered analog watch has a bold round dial that measures 42 mm in diameter. The stylish time markers and three time display hands are accompanied by pretty sun graphics that add to the appeal of the watch. The dial of the watch is protected by tough sapphire glass that is resistant to scratches. The stainless steel bezel has multilayers with bold cuts. The dial and bezel are held on a 9.8 mm thick stainless steel case. The classy stainless steel strap looks absolutely elegant on your wrist and the push button clasp holds the watch securely in place. To add the final dash of stellar charm the watch features a crown with Swarovski elements. The watch weighs a total of 92 g and is perfectly comfortable to wear all day long.

Functions and Other Features

Along with beauty and charm the Sheen analog watch presents practical features that come handy in daily life. The date display prevents the need to rummage through your bag to find your phone to ensure the date. The water resistance of the watch makes it ideal for daily wear. The watch also has the moonphase feature matches the night-time themed watch and helps you keep track of of the stages of the moon.
The charming Casio Sheen Analog Watch is a beautiful watch that is bound to make a stellar impression when you wear it.

column1: Watches are the perfect way to complement the clothes you wear. Are you looking for a simple and elegant watch that can stand up to the demands of daily use
column2: yet be stylish enough to wear on those classy evenings out? Perhaps
column3: you think of a watch as an accessory and aim to add a few more to that collection of yours. Whatever the need may be
column4:
the Maxima analog watch for women seems to be the appropriate choice. This casual watch from Maxima sports a classy analog dial driven by a battery powered quartz mechanism that keeps both you and the watch ticking right through the day. 

Body and Design

column1: The analog watch from Maxima comes with a leather strap. The leather strap makes this watch very comfortable to wear over long periods of time. The watch also features a rectangular dial that is encased in a steel bezel. The simplistic design of the rectangular dial
column3:
really accentuates the beauty of such a watch.

Functions and Other Features

column1: The women's analog watch from Maxima is designed to be water resistant as well as water resistant to a depth of 30 m
column2: making your next trip to one of those scenic waterfalls even more enjoyable.

column4: which uses small bar shaped crystals of quartz or silicon dioxide as it is otherwise referred to as.

column1: The functioning of the Quartz timepieces like this Casio analog women’s watch makes use of quartz crystals to provide a very accurate resonator which gives a constant electronic signal for timekeeping purposes. These quartz crystals work by generating an electrical charge which causes them to vibrate at a thousand times a second
column2: making them extremely stable resonators for extremely accurate timekeeping. The biggest advantage of employing this quartz crystal technology is its operational simplicity and accuracy
column3:

column1: This dial is surrounded by a considerably sturdy stainless steel case which provides the dial with sizeable protection against low intensity impacts and shock. The entire dial and case configuration on this watch is held firmly on your wrist with a very impressive and effective stainless steel bracelet strap. This stainless steel strap with a 21 mm band width sports a very similar look and finish as the dial’s case and the watch hands

column1: The Sheen series of Casio caters to an audience who is looking for an exemplary timepiece that can combine unrivalled functionality with incredibly sophisticated looks. Most watches today either have one or the other

This here is the analog watch for women from Casio and it is just one such product from the brand that effortlessly manages to give you an incredibly good-looking timepiece along with the highest levels of practicality. Powered by a battery and kept ticking in time by a quartz mechanism
column3:
the analog women’s Casio wristwatch is the ideal accessory to sport when you want to add a little style to the clothes you wear on a daily basis.

Body and Design

column1: Designed to accentuate the clothes and accessories you wear
column2: the Sheen series women’s wristwatch from Casio truly makes for a very practical daily wear accessory. The designers of the timepiece have equipped the round shaped dial with lustrous rhinestone hour markers that highlight the faint hue of the dial’s background. In addition
column3: for that added sense of sophistication and style
column4: the wristwatch features a rhinestone studded bezel as well.

column1: To prevent the movement and mechanism of the Casio women’s analog timepiece from being affected by accidental spills and knocks
column2: the wristwatch features a rather robust stainless steel case and bezel. Moreover
column3: to prevent scratches from finding its way onto the dial when the watch is stored in your handbag
column4: the designers from Casio have given it a mineral glass dial window.

column1: The Sheen series women’s analog Casio wristwatch makes use of a plush leather strap to meet all your watch-wearing comfort requirements. In addition
column2: to make sure that the wristwatch does not slip off your wrist when you play your weekend game of tennis or badminton
column3:
the strap features a push button clasp.

Functions and Other Features

column1: As a practical daily wear accessory
column2: the women’s Sheen series analog Casio wristwatch is designed with a couple of features and functions to help you make it through your day a little easier. For example
column3: the water-resistant timepiece features an analog day and date display along with a 24-hour dial to help you always stay up-to-date and on time for all your meetings and events that you have planned. Whichever way you look at it
column4: the analog women’s Casio wristwatch from the Sheen series is an exemplary product from the brand and it should
column6: make for the perfect addition to your collection of exquisite watches.

column1: Watches have evolved over the years to redefine fashion accessories and set style trends. Watches of the Sheen series from Casio are no exception to the trend. The Casio Ladies' Analog watch has a sophisticated watch face

column1: The dial is housed within a steel case that adds to the elegant appearance of the time telling device from Casio. Resistant to corrosive substances
column2: the steel case ensures that your timepiece is durable against wear and tear. The attractive steel frame along with the steel cord lend this timepiece a ravishing look. Moreover

column2:
without causing any irritation to your soft skin.

column1: From this glamourous line comes a watch that women are certainly going to go gaga over. The Casio Sheen Analog Watch for Women is what you wear when you want to get heads turning. The stylish design of the battery powered watch makes it the perfect accessory to pair with the casual clothes you wear when you go out to the movies and even those high-fashion outfits you wear to club. This watch isn’t just about looks. Like the woman who is a perfect mix of beauty and brawn the Casio Sheen watch is the perfect mix of style and precision. The impeccable quartz mechanism ensures that you can be on time or fashionably late
column2:
but never the one who is tardy.

Body and Design

column1:
The Casio Sheen Analog watch with steel cord comes with a bold round dial that has been glammed up with designer hour markers and stylish time display hands to match. A mineral glass dial window keeps the watch safe from scratches when you party hard or when you wrestle for the last piece of pizza with friends. To protect the inner mechanism of the watch is a durable steel case. The leather strap comes with a fold over clasp to hold the watch securely on your wrist.

Functions and Other Features
The rains may wash up the perfect outdoor party
column2: but you don’t have to run for cover in worry that your glamourous watch will die on you. The Casio Sheen Analog watch is water resistant up to 30 m making it resistant to rain and splashes. The watch also comes with the handy day and date display that appear in offset dials.

column1: The Casio Sheen Analog wristwatch if for the woman who loves all things glitzy and glamourous. Every day is made special when you don this stunning watch and tread ahead in life with style

column1: Stunning
column2: timeless and ultra-sophisticated is this wristwatch that hails from Casio’s ultra-stylish and highly fashionable standard range of Sheen analog watches for women. A perfect choice for the fashion forward modern day woman
column3:
this exquisitely designed watch is sure to help you express a strong sense of grace and elegance. This battery powered women’s watch from the house of Casio works on the popular time keeping technology that makes use of small bar shaped crystals of quartz or silicon dioxide.

Body and Design

column1: This highly aesthetic watch from Casio’s Sheen collection comes with a round dial measuring 39 mm in diameter and 10.2 mm in thickness and contains a light coloured watch face. Apart from the regular time tracking
column2: this multi-functional watch is also capable of keeping track of other highly important values and measurements.

column1: The watch’s multi-functional dial is surrounded by a sturdy stainless steel case
column2: which along with a rhinestone studded stainless steel bezel provides the dial with a considerable amount of durability and impact resistance. The dial is held in comfortably and securely attached to your wrist with the help of the watch’s trendy leather strap
column3: which operates an efficient push button clasp. With a strong stainless steel composition and an array of functionalities
column4:
this specialized women’s Casio Sheen Analog Watch manages to weigh just 48 g.

Functions and Other Features

column1: The three analog chronograph sub-dials contained within the main dial are responsible for displaying or indicating the <strong>24-hour time format
column2: date and stopwatch readings. All the necessary changes or adjustments to the time
column3: date or day can be done through the watch’s rotating screw crown and the two push buttons which are found on the right side of the dial’s case.

column1: The dial’s mineral glass cover along with the dial’s sturdy stainless steel case gives the watch a water-resistant capability. With such sophistication and elegance clubbed with significant amount of multi-functionality
column2: this women’s watch from Casio is sure to find its way and be part of your esteemed watch collection.

column1: An amalgamation of enigmatic elegance and efficient performance
column2: the watches from the Casio Sheen series are designed to add a tinge of glamour to the wearer’s personality.

column1: This exquisite ladies’ watch of the Sheen series is designed elegantly to add a dazzle to your appearance. The battery-powered analog watch will earn you admiring glances from people at any party. The timekeeping mechanism of this adorable timepiece is regulated by the electro-oscillations of quartz crystals
column2:
which make sure you are always on time for appointments.

Body and Design

column1: The round dial of this watch has a spectacular appearance
column2: making the Casio watch an item of desire. Encrusted with Swarovski elements on the ceramic bezel
column3: this gorgeous analog Casio watch for women is an eye-catcher in a crowd. Moreover
column4: the watch face is decorated with sun graphics
column5: which make this dazzling timepiece even more endearing.

column1: A sapphire glass cover on the dial makes the watch face resistant to scratches thus protecting your prized time wear from accidental damages. Furthermore
column2: the screw lock back accentuates the enigmatic sheen of this classy timepiece.

column1: To further prevent any chances of damage to your Casio Sheen analog watch
column2: the timepiece is equipped with a stainless steel case. The sturdy watch case also adds a touch of elegance to your appearance. The stainless steel case is resistant to corrosion
column3: thus enhancing the longevity of this timepiece.

column1: A solid stainless steel strap keeps your precious timepiece fastened to your wrist without the slightest discomfiture. The cumbersome process of wearing and removing the watch is eased due to the presence of a One-touch 3-fold Buckle clasp
column2:
which enables you to take the timepiece off your wrist just by pressing a button.

Functions and Other Features

column1: This magnificent time wear of the Sheen series from Casio also boasts of an excellent performance. You can wear this watch as you do the dishes in the kitchen after a party; this wonderful timepiece will not be affected. The watch is water resistant up to a depth of 50 m and can withstand a few splashes of water.
Not only does the Casio Sheen watch tell you what day of the month it is
column2: but it also informs you of the phases of the moon. Next time you wish to prepare for some holy ritual
column3: consulting the almanac for the moonphase will not be necessary.

column1: Apart from displaying the time in 24 hour format
column2: this multifunctional watch can be used as a stopwatch too. The analog chronograph function enables you to time your sports activities
column3: thus allowing you the scope for improvement. The Casio Sheen women’s watch is a classic example of technological brilliance and will always charm you with its features.

A sapphire glass on the watch face protects the watch from scratches. The stainless steel bezel accentuates the beauty of the dial in the most unique way.

Functions and Other Features

column1: This watch is water-resistant up to 50 m which means when you decide to give your playful dog a bath the water does not affect your watch. A woman carries her entire world in her handbag but digging through your bag to your find your phone
column2: or other devices to tell the date or day can be very annoying. And so it is comforting to know that you have access to this essential information on a device strapped to your wrist
column3: as the Casio Analog watch comes with day and date display.

column1: Nature is mankind’s greatest source of artistic inspiration and results in something truly beautiful. A perfect example for nature inspired creativity would be the Casio Sheen Analog Watch for Women that has drawn inspiration from the stunning night sky that is studded with stars. This charmingly elegant watch is for the woman whose personality is as bright as star
column2:
whose generosity is as radiant like the moon but whose core is as tough as steel. The multi-purpose Sheen Analog sports Watch is the perfect accessory to pair with your casual and formal clothes and even great for those high-fashion clothes you sport from time to time.

Body and Design

column1:
The battery powered analog watch has a bold round dial that measures 42 mm in diameter. The stylish time markers and three time display hands are accompanied by pretty sun graphics that add to the appeal of the watch. The dial of the watch is protected by tough sapphire glass that is resistant to scratches. The stainless steel bezel has multilayers with bold cuts. The dial and bezel are held on a 9.8 mm thick stainless steel case. The classy stainless steel strap looks absolutely elegant on your wrist and the push button clasp holds the watch securely in place. To add the final dash of stellar charm the watch features a crown with Swarovski elements. The watch weighs a total of 92 g and is perfectly comfortable to wear all day long.

Functions and Other Features

Along with beauty and charm the Sheen analog watch presents practical features that come handy in daily life. The date display prevents the need to rummage through your bag to find your phone to ensure the date. The water resistance of the watch makes it ideal for daily wear. The watch also has the moonphase feature matches the night-time themed watch and helps you keep track of of the stages of the moon.
The charming Casio Sheen Analog Watch is a beautiful watch that is bound to make a stellar impression when you wear it.

column1: Here is a fun

This beautiful watch is a Q&Q Silicone Strap Analog watch for women. This trendy and sassy watch is comes as part of  Q&Q's  highly popular Silicone Strap series of analog watches.

column1: This analog watch has been designed for sports occasions and events
column2: making it a n ideal match to go with your track pants and sweatshirt as you make your way to the gym or a morning jog. This attractive Q&Q Silicone Strap Watch keeps track of time by using the popular quartz crystal technology
column3:
as the crystals provide a stable resonator which gives a constant electronic signal for the purpose of accurate timekeeping. 

Body and Design

column1:
This Q&Q Silicone Strap Analog watch for women comes with a gently rounded dial that looks appealing on a sports watch. The dial is encased in a plastic case that gives the watch a well-rounded and tidy appearance while augmenting the sporty tone of the watch. The watch comes with a plastic strap that increases the durability of this watch as the watch can be easily fastened or unfastened as you desire. The inclusion of a mineral glass cover provides great optical clarity and an added degree of damage-resistance to the dial.

Functions and Other Features

Water resistant
column2: this Q&Q Silicone Strap Analog watch for women comes with minimal splashing waterproof
column3: which means that a few accidental splashes from a beverage will not affect the functioning of this watch. A few drops of rain that hit your watch when you are caught in a sudden downpour on your way home from work will not hinder its functioning. This Q&Q Silicone Strap Analog watch for women is a great watch that works as a wonderful timekeeping accessory for all your sports events while significantly enhancing the your personal sense of style.

column1: Show a woman the lovely Q&Q analog watch and she will be drawn to it like a moth to a flame. This lovely Q&Q analog watch has been created for women who love a little hint of all things pretty and shiny in their look. The most appealing trait of this watch is that you can use it to dress up or dress down any outfit. You can easily pair this attractive watch with your party clothes. Just strap the watch with that black halter neck dress and put on the Q&Q watch and you are good to go.

The analog watch also pairs perfectly well with your jeans and cute T-shirts giving you a well balanced outfit for a casual dinner date with friends. This trendy watch makes every woman look dashing and best of all it is a watch that doesn’t need you to change your wardrobe.

Body and Design

The Q&Q watch sports a rectangular dial with designer patterns to add to its appeal. The small yet distinct time markers and the three hands help you tell time with ease. These elements have been carefully designed to enhance the art on the dial. A curved glass cover protects the dial giving it a smooth look.
The sturdy alloy case that envelopes the dial is studded with clear stones and so has the bezel
column2:
giving you two layers of lustrous charm. To hold the timepiece firmly on your wrist is the elegant leather strap that gently touches your skin making the watch comfortable to wear for long hours.

Functions and Other Features

column1: To match your vibrant personality and spontaneous bouts of adventure the watch is water resistant allowing you to dash through rain when you feel like it or be generous and help your mom with the dishes before you leave for your night out with friends.

The Q&Q analog watch is for every woman who is upbeat and vibrant. When you want to dial up the glamour and look trendy and stylish a simple way to do it would be to pair your outfit with the Q&Q Analog Watch.

column1: As a glittering symbol of great craftsmanship and heightened aesthetics is this beautifully conceived timepiece from Q&Q’s highly desirable line of women’s analog watches. An ideal choice of personal timekeepers for the trendy and fashion conscious woman
column2: this analog watch from Q&Q accentuates in its wearer a sense of beauty and elegance
column3:
making it an automatic selection for all your casual events or parties.

Body and Design

column1: The incredibly trendy women’s wristwatch from Q&Q features a fashionable rectangular dial that houses an attractive yet mellow background colour. This plain and solid coloured background features a metallic coloured design to disrupt the monotony of the watch face. The outermost track on the watch face carries the dial’s timekeeping markings in a dark colour; while the three watch hands carry a bright metallic colour. This clever use of different colours on the watch face
column2: especially against such a light colour give you great dial visibility for easy time reading.

column1: This highly creative and beautifully put together dial is surrounded by a thick alloy case that is designed to provide the dial with an improved level of durability and damage resistance. An alloy is a mixture that is composed of two or more metals
column2: which in this case is aimed at producing a metal alloy that stronger and lighter than the original metal elements. This highly specialized alloy case while protecting the dial also contributes to the watch’s aesthetic value with its bright metallic finish which is encrusted with an array of stones or crystals.

column1: The top and bottom portions of the bright metallic stone-studded alloy case have provision which allows the case to be attached to the watch’s classy and sensual leather strap that carries the same colour as the watch face. This stylish leather strap is wholly responsible for keeping this exquisite women’s personal timepiece comfortably perched to your wrist as long as you desire.

The dial on this Q&Q women’s analog watch is give a significant amount of protection in the form of a clear curved glass. All the time related changes or alterations on the dial can easily be made using the watch’s rotating screw crown found on the right side of the dial’s alloy case. The combination of the dial’s alloy case along with the curved glass cover gives the dial a substantial water-resistant ability. This high durability with water-resistance makes sure that the watch is more than capable of brushing off that occasional drop or that unexpected spray of water that is headed your way.
Together
